enus%2C%20and%20apps.%20The%20Omni%20Mini%20LED's%20homepage%20also%20suffers%20from%20ugly%20advertising%20front%20and%20center.%20On%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20I%20do%20like%20the%20TV's%20Alexa%20integration%2C%20which%20makes%20it%20easy%20to%20use%20the%20display%20to%20control%20other%20compatible%20smart%20home%20devices.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20can%20look%20beyond%20the%20Fire%20TV%20OS'%20shortcomings%20and%20avoid%20enabling%20some%20of%20the%20TV's%20superfluous%20features%2C%20the%20Omni%20Mini%20LED%20is%20a%20good%20midrange%20offering.%20It's%20easily%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Fbest-tv%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebest%20TV%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20Amazon's%20lineup.%20However%2C%20it's%20a%20bit%20pricey%20compared%20to%20similar%20offerings%20from%20TCL%20and%20Hisense%2C%20so%20I%20recommend%20snagging%20this%20set%20when%20it's%20discounted%20during%20one%20of%20Amazon's%20sales.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%223b2e5799-0a1e-48b8-89a2-b852a43ba48b%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Specs%20and%20setup%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ESpecifications%20are%20competitive%20for%20this%20class%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20close-up%20of%20the%20Amazon%20Omni%20Mini%20LED%20TV's%20left%20foot%20stand.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67d728cd585f1dff88b24abe%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221875%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20TV's%20feet%20lift%20the%20display%20high%20enough%20to%20fit%20an%20average%20soundbar%20in%20front.%3Cp%3EDavid%20Murphy%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAmazon's%20Fire%20TV%20Omni%20Mini%20LED%20TV%20has%20all%20the%20specs%20you%20should%20expect%20from%20a%20model%20in%20this%20class.%20The%20TV%20is%20available%20in%20four%20different%20sizes%20%E2%80%94%2055%2C%2065%2C%2075%2C%20or%2085%20inches.%20All%20four%20options%20use%20a%20QLED