0Prime%20Video).%20The%20antenna%20isn't%20included%2C%20naturally%2C%20but%20it's%20an%20inexpensive%20add-on%20if%20you%20don't%20want%20to%20pay%20a%20monthly%20fee%20for%20local%20channels.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20TV%20also%20does%20a%20great%20job%20of%20managing%20other%20critical%20gear%20in%20your%20home%20entertainment%20center%2C%20like%20your%20cable%2Fsatellite%20box%20and%20receiver.%20I%20had%20no%20issues%20getting%20the%20Omni%20Mini%20LED%20synced%20with%20my%20Denon%20AV%20receiver%2C%20and%20the%20TV's%20HDMI%20eARC%20connection%20allowed%20me%20to%20use%20the%20included%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3FamazonTrackingID%3Dbi-auto-74882-20%26h%3D42baa5ab0f01eca2e8b80a07f8b5b38b62176056f3d6811367fb776bf881da08%26postID%3D67d7231b4e85a4b1498acb31%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Ftech%252Famazon-fire-tv-omni-mini-led-review%26site%3Dbi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.amazon.com%252FAlexa-Remote-requires-compatible-Amazon%252Fdp%252FB0B9HX4TGV%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAlexa%20Voice%20Remote%20Enhanced%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20power%20the%20receiver%20on%20and%20off.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20also%20easy%20to%20control%20the%20receiver's%20volume%20using%20the%20remote%2C%20and%20the%20TV%20comes%20with%20plenty%20of%20options%20for%20fine-tuning%20infrared%20controls%20to%20support%20all%20kinds%20of%20different%20setups.%20That%20said%2C%20I%20wish%20Amazon%20had%20thrown%20its%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3FamazonTrackingID%3Dbi-auto-74882-20%26h%3D6889493c018a47c6ebe7e719ae6feb4f09cbfc4615f87766bd24f01dc661d9f7%26postID%3D67d7231b4e85a4b1498acb31%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Ftech%252Famazon-fire-tv-omni-mini-led-review%26site%3Dbi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.amazon.com%252FIntroducing-alexa-voice-remote-pro%252Fdp%252FB09RX4HKTD%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAlexa%20Voice%20Remote%20Pro%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20box%20instead.%20The%20Pro%20Remote%20is%20a%20fun%20upgrade%20that%20has%20backlit%20buttons%20and%20a%20lost%20remote%20chime.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELike%20most%20TVs%2C%20Amazon's%20Omni%20Mini%20LED%204K%20is%20packed%20with%20adjustable%20settings.%20The%20most%20critical%20one%20is%20found%20within%20the%20display%20settings%20menu%2C%20where%20you'll%20get%20a%20number%20of%20different%20presets%20to%20choose%20from%20depending%20on%20what%20you're%20watching%20(SDR%2C%20HDR%2C%20Dolby%20Vision%2C%20etc.).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20get%20the%20most%20accurate%20performance%20out%20of%20the%20box%2C%20I%20recommend%20selecting%20the%20aptly%20named%20Filmmaker%20mode%20for%20everything%20you%20do.%20Of%20course%2C%20if%20you%20don't%20like%20the%20look%20of%20FilmMaker%20mode%2C%20you%20can%20select%20from%20several%20other%20presets%2C%20such%20as%20Standard%2C%20Movie%20Bright%2C%20Movie%20Dark%2C%20and%20Vivid.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22262868f1-6c82-4279-9563-23865ea8e60c%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Picture%20performance%5C%22%3EThe%20TV%20delivers%20solid%20color%20accuracy%2C%20but%20there%20are%20brighter%20sets%20that%20cost%20less%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222184%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22An%20angled%20view%20of%20a%20Fire%20TV%20Mini%20LED%20display%20on%20a%20media%20console%20in%20a%20living%20room.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67d729f469253ccddf99661b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221638%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Fire%20TV%20Omni%20Mini%20LED%20has%20noticeably%20better%20picture%20quality%20than%20Amazon's%20other%20smart%20TV%20models.%3Cp%3EDavid%20Murphy%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20evaluate%20the%20Fire%20TV%20Omni%20Mini%20LED's%20image%20quality%2C%20I%20used%20test%20patterns%20and%20watched%20various%20movies%20and%20TV%20shows.%20I%20measured%20the%20display's%20HDR%20picture%20accuracy%20in%20Filmmaker%20mode%20using%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.portrait.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPortrait%20Displays'%20Calman%20software%3C%2Fa%3E.%20What%20I%20found%20was%20that%20the%20TV's%20grayscale%20and%20color%20performance%20both%20delivered%20solid%20accuracy%20out%20of%20the%20box.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20Filmmaker%20mode%2C%20the%20TV%20delivered%20an%20average%20DeltaE%20of%202.7%20for%20grayscale%20and%202.5%20for%20color.%20These%20measurements%20describe%20how%20far%20away%20a%20tested%20color%20is%20from%20what%20its%20true%20value%20should%20be.%20A%20DeltaE%20under%20three%20is%20what%20you're%20looking%20for%3B%20the%20higher%20you%20go%20over%20five%2C%20the%20more%20noticeable%20color%20errors%20become.%20So%2C%20the%20Omni%20Mini%20LED's%20Filmmaker%20mode%20is%20quite%20good.%20However%2C%20the%20same%20can't%20be%20said%20for%20the%20TV's%20other%20presets.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20switched%20to%20the%20Standard%20picture%20mode%20with%20HDR%20enabled%20and%20remeasured%2C%20it%20was%20practically%20night%20and%20day.%20I%20recorded%20an%20average%20DeltaE%20of%208.6%20for%20grayscale%20and%207.9%20for%20colors.%20The%20TV's%20Movie%20Bright%20and%20Movie%20Dark%20modes%20didn't%20fare%20any%20better%20than%20Standard.%20The%20Vivid%20preset%2C%20though%20eye-poppingly%20saturated%2C%20was%20twice%20as%20bad%20for%20accuracy%20as%20Standard%20%E2%80%94%20virtually%20unusable%20unless%20you%20heavily%20favor%20brightness%20over%20accuracy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20I%20don't%20say%20that%20to%20be%20flippant.%20Even%20in%20Filmmaker%20mode%2C%20I%20found%20myself%20wishing%20the%20TV%20had%20a%20little%20more%20saturation%20in%20certain%20scenes%2C%20like%20during%20lightsaber%20battles%20in%20the%20latest%20%26quot%3BStar%20Wars%26quot%3B%20films%20and%20TV%20shows.%20That's%20easy%20enough%20to%20adjust%20using%20the%20Omni%20Mini%20LED's%20various%20settings%2C%20but%20Filmmaker%20mode%20is%20a%20great%20starting%20point%20for%20viewers%20who%20favor%20an%20accurate%20image.%20There's%20also%20an%20%26quot%3BIntelligent%20Picture%26quot%3B%20feature%20that%20can%20change%20settings%20like%20brightness%20and%20color%20intensity%20based%20on%20a%20sensor%20that%20evaluates%20your%20room's%20conditions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20TV's%20local%20dimming%20feature%20defaults%20to%20different%20levels%20depending%20on%20the%20format%20of%20whatever%20you're%20watching%2C%20but%20you%20can%20manually%20adjust%20it%20to%20your%20taste.%20I%20found%20the%20high%20setting%20made%20the%20TV's%20contrast%20feel%20overwhelming%20when%20watching%20Dolby%20Vision%20HDR%20movies%20like%20%26quot%3BDune.%26quot%3B%20I%20ended%20up%20settling%20on%20medium%20for%20the%20best%20balance%2C%20as%20this%20yielded%20rich%2C%20vibrant%20visuals%20without%20making%20it%20feel%20like%20I%20was%20staring%20into%20the%20sun.%20I%20didn't%20notice%20any%20egregious%20signs%20of%20blooming%20(halos%20around%20bright%20objects)%20with%20the%20set%20in%20this%20dimming%20mode.%20Instead%2C%20when%20the%20Harkonnens%20sacked%20Arrakis%20in%20%26quot%3BDune%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Omni%20Mini%20LED%20presented%20the%20epic%20battle%20with%20great%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Fwhat-is-hdr-tv%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EHDR%20imagery%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20impressive%20HDR%20performance%20is%2C%20in%20part%2C%20the%20result%20of%20the%20Omni%20Mini%20LED's%20solid%20brightness%20capabilities.%20I%20measured%20the%20TV's%20brightness%20across%20both%20SDR%20and%20HDR%20signals.%20In%20Filmmaker%20mode%2C%20a%2010%25%20window%20reached%20a%20peak%20of%201%2C058%20nits%20in%20HDR%20using%20the%20default%2070%25%20backlight%20setting.%20When%20I%20cranked%20the%20backlight%20to%20100%25%20on%20Filmmaker%20mode%2C%20the%20TV's%20peak%20brightness%20increased%20to%201%2C422%20nits.%20When%20I%20blasted%20the%20entire%20screen%20with%20a%20white%20box%2C%20the%20TV%20was%20able%20to%20display%20a%20max%20of%20694%20nits.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20also%20repeated%20the%20same%20tests%20for%20SDR%2C%20which%20is%20the%20mode%20that%20most%20broadcast%20TV%20sources%2C%20like%20cable%20and%20satellite%2C%20often%20use.%20I%20measured%20714%20nits%20on%20default%20settings%20with%20a%2010%25%20window%2C%20and%20958%20nits%20when%20I%20maximized%20the%20backlight.%20On%20a%20completely%20white%20screen%2C%20the%20maximum%20measured%20brightness%20dropped%20to%20380%20and%20515%20nits%2C%20respectively.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThose%20brightness%20numbers%20are%20solid%20for%20a%20TV%20in%20this%20class%2C%20and%20they're%20more%20than%20double%20what%20Amazon's%20step-down%20Fire%20TV%20Omni%20QLED%20can%20deliver.%20This%20level%20of%20brightness%20is%20enough%20to%20deliver%20great%20HDR%20performance%20and%20help%20overcome%20glare%20in%20rooms%20with%20lots%20of%20windows.%20However%2C%20the%20TV%20does%20track%20a%20little%20bit%20below%20expected%20brightness%20levels%20for%20low-to-medium%20shades%20of%20gray.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20also%20important%20to%20note%20that%20the%20Omni%20Mini%20LED%20isn't%20the%20brightest%20or%20most%20eye-catching%20TV%20at%20its%20price%20point.%20For%20instance%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Ftcl-qm7-qled-4k-tv-review%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETCL%20QM7%20Mini%20LED%20TV%3C%2Fa%3E%20offers%20a%20peak%20of%20around%201%2C700%20nits%20in%20HDR.%20The%20QM7%20launched%20for%20around%20the%20same%20price%20as%20the%20Omni%20Mini%20LED%20last%20year%2C%20but%20it's%20now%20sold%20for%20a%20lot%20less.%20From%20a%20picture%20quality%20standpoint%2C%20similarly%20priced%20sets%20from%20brands%20like%20TCL%20and%20Hisense%20have%20a%20slight%20edge%20over%20Amazon's%20TV.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%220612b5ba-51db-4ad1-9ec0-ce5d15e8bc77%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Alexa%20capabilities%5C%22%3EAlexa%20integration%20works%20great%20for%20controlling%20your%20smart%20devices%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20close-up%20of%20the%20Alexa%20indicator%20on%20the%20Amazon%20Omni%20Mini%20LED%20TV.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67d72860b8b41a9673facc9a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221875%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EYou%20can%20access%20Alexa%20via%20hands-free%20microphones%20built%20into%20the%20TV.%3Cp%3EDavid%20Murphy%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Omni%20Mini%20LED%20integrates%20the%20full%20powers%20of%20Alexa%20directly%20into%20the%20TV.%20You%20can%20speak%20prompts%20to%20the%20digital%20assistant%20whether%20your%20TV's%20screen%20is%20on%20or%20off%2C%20and%20it'll%20reply%20via%20the%20built-in%20speakers.%20However%2C%20if%20you're%20connected%20to%20a%20separate%20sound%20system%2C%20like%20a%20receiver%20or%20soundbar%2C%20those%20components%20will%20need%20to%20be%20left%20on%20in%20order%20to%20hear%20Alexa.%20If%20your%20TV%20is%20on%20when%20you're%20talking%20to%20Alexa%2C%20you%20may%20even%20get%20a%20visual%20element%20on%20the%20screen%20to%20complement%20whatever%20you%20asked%20(for%20example%2C%20a%20week's%20worth%20of%20weather%20temperatures%20and%20condition%20icons).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20TV%20also%20gives%20you%20the%20same%20smart%20home%20powers%20you'd%20get%20from%20a%20conventional%20Echo%20speaker%20or%20display.%20This%20means%20you%20can%20set%20up%20all%20your%20compatible%20smart%20gear%20within%20the%20Alexa%20app%20and%20then%20adjust%20temperatures%2C%20turn%20lights%20on%20and%20off%2C%20and%20open%20garage%20doors%20%E2%80%94%20to%20name%20a%20few%20%E2%80%94%20by%20talking%20to%20your%20TV.%20You%20can%20even%20connect%20compatible%20security%20cameras%20and%20pull%20up%20a%20live%20feed%20directly%20on%20the%20display.%20(Sadly%2C%20there's%20no%20way%20to%20automatically%20turn%20the%20TV%20on%20with%20a%20live%20feed%20from%20a%20camera%20if%20it%2C%20say%2C%20sees%20someone%20at%20the%20front%20door.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Fire%20TV%20Omni%20Mni%20LED%20also%20supports%20Amazon's%20Ambient%20Experience.%20This%20feature%20is%20essentially%20a%20screensaver%20that%20can%20turn%20on%20by%20itself%20whenever%20the%20TV%20detects%20movement%20in%20the%20room.%20This%20feature%20is%20also%20available%20on%20the%20cheaper%20Omni%20QLED%20model%20and%20some%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Famazon-fire-tv-buying-guide%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EFire%20TV%20streaming%20devices%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Unfortunately%2C%20I%20didn't%20find%20this%20function%20to%20be%20all%20that%20useful.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20it's%20meant%20to%20transform%20the%20TV%20into%20an%20art%20display%20of%20sorts%2C%20it's%20awkward%20to%20use.%20You%20can%20only%20pick%20a%20single%2C%20top-level%20category%20of%20images%20or%20movies%20you%20want%20to%20display%20(no%20mixing%20%26quot%3BMovies%20and%20TV%26quot%3B%20with%20%26quot%3BCloudscapes%2C%26quot%3B%20for%20example).%20And%20the%20simple%20act%20of%20changing%20these%20categories%20isn't%20very%20intuitive.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20it%20stands%2C%20the%20feature%20doesn't%20feel%20like%20it's%20worth%20the%20120%20watts%20or%20so%20of%20power%20it%20consumes%20when%20it's%20active.%20If%20you%20truly%20want%20a%20TV-turned-art%20display%2C%20you're%20better%20off%20with%20something%20like%20Samsung's%20Frame%2C%20which%20automatically%20fires%20up%20a%20low-power%20mode%20when%20it's%20being%20artsy%20and%20offers%20access%20to%20Samsung's%20extensive%20Art%20Store%20(albeit%20for%20a%20subscription%20fee).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2292c0556d-ee4c-46c5-bcb0-00ec38f4345d%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Fire%20TV%20OS%5C%22%3EThe%20Fire%20TV%20OS%20gets%20the%20job%20done%2C%20but%20the%20amount%20of%20advertising%20is%20irritating%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22An%20Amazon%20Omni%20Mini%20LED%20TV%20displaying%20an%20ad%20for%20Nestle%20Crunch%20chocolate%20on%20the%20homepage.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67d72936b8b41a9673facca6%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221875%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20number%20of%20ads%20that%20the%20Fire%20TV%20OS%20cycles%20through%20is%20annoying.%3Cp%3EDavid%20Murphy%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20know%20the%20Fire%20TV%20OS%20has%20its%20fans%2C%20but%20to%20me%2C%20the%20interface%20just%20feels%20cluttered%20and%20lacking.%20It%20still%20gets%20the%20job%20done%20for%20basic%20streaming%20needs%2C%20but%20I%20prefer%20Apple%20TV%2C%20Roku%2C%20and%20Google%20streaming%20devices%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEvery%20time%20you%20turn%20on%20your%20Fire%20TV%2C%20the%20first%20screen%20you'll%20see%20is%20Amazon's%20landing%20page.%20This%20page%20has%20a%20giant%20rotating%20section%20at%20the%20top%20that%20displays%20aggressive%20promotions%20for%20shows%20you%20can%20watch%20or%20services%20you%20can%20sign%20up%20for.%20What's%20worse%2C%20though%2C%20is%20that%20it%20even%20shows%20advertisements%20for%20brands%20like%20AAA%20and%20Progressive.%20I%20get%20content%20ads%2C%20but%20why%20is%20my%20TV%20trying%20to%20sell%20me%20insurance%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESadly%2C%20the%20underwhelming%20experience%20doesn't%20stop%20there.%20When%20I%20first%20clicked%20down%20on%20the%20remote%20to%20find%20movies%20and%20shows%20to%20watch%20on%20the%20homepage%2C%20the%20next%20row%20of%20icons%20highlighted%20content%20from%20a%20service%20called%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2FFawesome.tv%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EFawesome.tv%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%26quot%3B%20which%20I'd%20never%20heard%20of.%20Clicking%20on%20any%20of%20the%20titles%20prompted%20me%20to%20download%20a%20separate%20%26quot%3BFawesome%26quot%3B%20app%2C%20which%2C%20as%20it%20turns%20out%2C%20is%20an%20ad-supported%20service.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBelow%20that%20listing%20was%20an