il%20did%20drugs%20regularly%20and%20one%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmeerut-saurabh-rajput-murder-cement-murder-she-must-be-hanged-merchant-navy-officers-in-laws-blame-daughter-7959216%5C%22%3Epossible%20reasons%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20they%20killed%20Saurabh%20was%20that%20he%20would%20%26quot%3Bstop%20their%20drug%20sessions%26quot%3B.%20Sahil's%20dependence%20on%20drugs%20also%20made%20him%20susceptible%20to%20one%20of%20Muskaan's%20sinister%20plans%20in%20the%20lead-up%20to%20the%20murder%20-%20she%20made%20an%20account%20on%20the%20social%20media%20messaging%20app%20Snapchat%20and%20managed%20to%20convince%20her%20lover%20that%20her%20dead%20mother%20was%20using%20it%20to%20speak%20to%20him.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20account%20was%20not%20in%20the%20name%20of%20Sahil's%20mother%20but%20the%20messages%20were%20sent%20by%20Muskaan%20in%20a%20way%20that%20she%20made%20him%20believe%20that%20his%20dead%20mother%20had%20reincarnated%20and%20was%20speaking%20to%20him.%20She%20used%20this%20as%20a%20means%20of%20controlling%20Sahil%20and%2C%20later%2C%20convincing%20him%20to%20kill%20her%20husband%2C%20Saurabh.%20The%20entire%20plotting%20was%20done%20by%20Muskaan%2C%20who%20hatched%20the%20murder%20plan%20in%20November%26quot%3B%20said%20Superintendent%20of%20Police%20(Meerut%20City)%20Ayush%20Vikram%20Singh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EElaborate%20Plan%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Singh%20said%20that%20after%20deciding%20to%20kill%20Saurabh%2C%20Muskaan%20began%20scouting%20for%20places%20where%20she%20could%20bury%20his%20body.%20She%20told%20her%20friends%20she%20needed%20to%20bury%20some%20material%20she%20had%20used%20in%20a%20puja%20(prayer%20ritual)%20and%20even%20asked%20where%20one%20could%20bury%20a%20body.%20But%20the%20friends%20did%20not%20help%20her%20find%20a%20place.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMuskaan%2C%20the%20police%20officer%20said%2C%20then%20found%20out%20that%20Saurabh%2C%20who%20had%20been%20working%20in%20London%20since%202023%2C%20would%20return%20to%20Meerut%20in%20February%20to%20celebrate%20the%20birthday%20of%20their%20six-year-old%20daughter.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOn%20February%2022%2C%20she%20bought%20two%20knives%20for%20Rs%20800%2C%20saying%20she%20needed%20them%20to%20cut%20chicken.%20She%20also%20pretended%20to%20have%20anxiety%20and%20went%20to%20a%20doctor%20to%20get%20a%20prescription.%20She%20then%20looked%20up%20the%20names%20of%20two%20medicines%20online%20that%20she%20could%20use%20to%20render%20Saurabh%20unconscious%20and%20added%20them%20to%20the%20prescription%20so%20she%20could%20purchase%20them%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Mr%20Singh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20officer%20said%20that%20Saurabh%20returned%20on%20February%2024%20and%2C%20the%20next%20day%2C%20Muskaan%20mixed%20the%20medicines%20in%20his%20alcohol%2C%20but%20he%20did%20not%20drink.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMuskaan%20and%20Sahil%20kept%20looking%20for%20an%20opportunity%20and%20stabbed%20Saurabh%20to%20death%20after%20drugging%20him%20on%20March%204.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EFailed%20Gambit%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESaurabh's%20family%20had%20not%20been%20on%20good%20terms%20with%20him%20since%20he%20had%20married%20Muskaan%20against%20their%20wish%20in%202016%20and%20then%20moved%20out%20of%20the%20house%20to%20live%20with%20her%20in%20a%20rented%20apartment.%20Mr%20Singh%20said%20this%20and%20the%20fact%20that%20he%20used%20to%20drink%20regularly%20had%20led%20to%20his%20family%20practically%20disowning%20him.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20used%20to%20go%20to%20his%20parents'%20house%20to%20eat%2C%20but%20they%20did%20not%20have%20much%20of%20a%20relationship.%20He%20used%20to%20stay%20away%20from%20the%20city%20for%20days%20and%20had%20been%20abroad%20for%20two%20years%2C%20but%20his%20family%20did%20not%20contact%20him%20much.%20Muskaan%20knew%20about%20this%20and%20she%20was%20banking%20on%20it%20to%20be%20abl