wo%20Options...%26quot%3B%3A%20Israeli%20Ambassador%20On%20Gaza%20War%20Solution%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20military%20campaign%20will%20continue%20in%20Gaza%20till%20there%20is%20a%20Gaza%20free%20of%20Hamas%2C%20Israeli%20Ambassador%20Reuven%20Azar%20told%20NDTV%20World%20today.%20The%2042-day%20temporary%20ceasefire%20agreement%20between%20Israel%20and%20Hamas%20is%20now%20over%20and%20Hamas%20has%20gone%20back%20on%20its%20promise%20of%20releasing%20the%20hostages%20kidnapped%20by%20the%20terrorist%20organisation.%20This%2C%20Mr%20Azar%20said%2C%20is%20a%20violation%20of%20the%20agreement%2C%20and%20hence%2C%20left%20Israel%20with%20no%20option%20but%20to%20resort%20to%20military%20pressure.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20can%20be%20a%20peace%20today%2C%20if%20Hamas%20agrees%20and%20abides%20by%20the%20conditions%20set%20out%20for%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Mr%20Azar%20explaining%20that%20the%20two%20main%20conditions%20include%20freeing%20all%20the%20remaining%20hostages%20and%20never%20to%20be%20able%20to%20arm%20itself%20to%20launch%20terrorist%20attacks%20on%20Israel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20Hamas%20doesn't%20want%20peace%2C%20he%20told%20NDTV%20World%2C%20citing%20the%20decision%20not%20to%20release%20the%20hostages.%20%26quot%3BHamas%20has%20rejected%20to%20proposals%20of%20the%20American%20mediator%20time%20and%20again.%20It%20simply%20refuses%20to%20release%20the%20hostages.%20There%20is%20no%20option%20left%20for%20Israel%20now%2C%20but%20to%20resort%20to%20military%20pressure.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMilitary%20pressure%20is%20effective%20and%20works%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20%26quot%3BIt%20is%20because%20of%20military%20pressure%20that%20195%20of%20the%20254%20hostages%20have%20been%20released%20in%20the%20first%20place.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20United%20States%20has%20%26quot%3Bfully%20backed%20Israel%26quot%3B%20in%20its%20efforts%20to%20rout%20Gaza%20of%20any%20terrorist%20elements%2C%20and%20bringing%20lasting%20peace%20to%20the%20region%20both%20for%20Jews%20as%20well%20as%20Palestinians.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIsrael%2C%20he%20said%2C%20will%20pursue%20its%20efforts%20to%20the%20desired%20outcome%20at%20any%20cost.%20%26quot%3BIf%20a%20solution%20is%20not%20found%20diplomatically%2C%20then%20we%20shall%20achieve%20it%20militarily%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReacting%20to%20condemnation%20globally%2C%20the%20Israeli%20Ambassador%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BCondemnations%20do%20not%20change%20facts.%20And%20the%20fact%20is%20that%20there%20is%20a%20terrorist%20organisation%20in%20the%20Gaza%20strip%20that%20continues%20to%20hold%20hostages.%20The%20hostages%20they%20are%20holding%20are%20not%20just%20those%20from%20Israel%2C%20but%20they%20are%20holding%20the%20entire%20Palestinian%20population%20hostage%20to%20its%20misdeeds.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHamas%20is%20taking%20control%20of%20the%20aid%20being%20sent%20and%20is%20in%20turn%20selling%20them%20to%20Palestinian%20people.%20They%20are%20trying%20to%20extort%20the%20people%20with%20the%20hope%20of%20pushing%20Israel%20to%20a%20surrender.%20This%20is%20simply%20not%20going%20to%20happen.%20It%20is%20ridiculous%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20making%20Tel%20Aviv's%20intentions%20clear.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInstead%20of%20condemning%20Israel%2C%20what%20we%20expect%20from%20a%20responsible%20international%20community%20is%20to%20%26quot%3Bput%20pressure%20on%20Hamas%2C%20and%20help%20push%20for%20efforts%20to%20create%20peace%20in%20the%20region.%20They%20should%20do%20that%20diplomatically%20by%20getting%20the%20top%20brass%20of%20Hamas%20out%20of%20Gaza%20and%20give%20hope%20to%20the%20Palestinian%20people%20by%20encouraging%20a%20new%20and%20moderate%20Palestinian%20leadership%20-%20one%20that%20will%20allow%20Gaza%20to%20be%20reestablished%20and%20rebuilt%20for%20the%20betterment%20future%20of%20its%20people.%20Such%20peace%20is%20what%20is%20of%20common%20interest.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAnyone%20from%20the%20international%20community%20who%20says%20that%20military%20pressure%20should%20not%20be%20used%20is%20basically%20wanting%20Israel%20to%20surrender%20to%20a%20terrorist%20organisation%20that%20will%20continue%20to%20have%20a%20grip%20on%20Gaza%20forever.%20That%20cannot%20be%20acceptable%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Ambassador%20said%20that%20%26quot%3BHamas%20has%20to%20understand%20that%20its%20control%20of%20the%20Gaza%20strip%20is%20over.%20They%20will%20have%20to%20relinquish%20power%20at%20any%20cost.%20Israel%20will%20allow%20for%20them%20to%20peacefully%20leave%20Gaza%20forever%2C%20to%20give%20a%20chance%20to%20the%20Palestinian%20people%20to%20have%20a%20better%20future.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHamas%20has%20now%20got%20only%20two%20options%20-%20One%20is%20to%20return%20to%20the%20diplomatic%20table%20in%20a%20constructive%20way%20and%20accept%20the%20terms.%20That%20will%20stop%20the%20military%20campaign.%20The%20other%20option%20is%20for%20them%20not%20to%20cooperate.%20What%20that%20will%20do%20is%20leave%20Israel%20with%20the%20option%20for%20a%20ground%20invasion%20throughout%20Gaza%20in%20order%20to%20completely%20clean%20it%20out%20of%20all%20terror%20elements%20linked%20to%20Hamas%20and%20then%20transfer%20authority%20of%20Gaza%20to%20a%20new%20moderate%20Palestinian%20leadership%20and%20to%20responsible%20international%20stakeholders%20who%20will%20help%20bring%20peace%20and%20prosperity%20in%20Gaza.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIsrael%20has%20the%20resolution%20and%20the%20resilience%20to%20do%20this%2C%20but%20I%20want%20to%20make%20it%20clear%20that%20we%20would%20prefer%20taking%20the%20first%20option%20-%20of%20diplomacy%20and%20dialogue.%20We%20will%20resort%20to%20option%20two%20only%20if%20Hamas%20refuses%20to%20cooperate.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Israeli%20Ambassador%20concluded%20by%20saying%20that%20%26quot%3BIn%20this%20holy%20month%20of%20Ramadan%20(Ramzan)%2C%20more%20than%2075%2C000%20Muslims%20come%20every%20single%20day%20to%20pray%20in%20the%20holy%20city%20of%20Jerusalem%20in%20Israel.%20We%20have%20always%20supported%20religious%20freedom.%20It%20is%20the%20terrorists%20who%20we%20go%20after.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHamas%20still%20holds%2059%20Israeli%20hostages%2C%20which%20it%20has%20so%20far%20refused%20to%20release.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1742386560000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-09%2Feuj9pmh_reuven-azar_625x300_24_September_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fhamas-has-only-two-options-israeli-ambassador-reuven-azar-on-gaza-war-solution-7960308%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20military%20campaign%20will%20continue%20in%20Gaza%20till%20there%20is%20a%20Gaza%20free%20of%20Hamas%2C%20Israeli%20Ambassador%20Reuven%20Azar%20told%20NDTV%20World%20today.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fhamas-has-only-two-options-israeli-ambassador-reuven-azar-on-gaza-war-solution-7960308%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'Cold-blooded%20murder'%3A%20Priyanka%20Gandhi%20flays%20Israel%20over%20Gaza%20strikes%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1742386320000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-119213774%2Cimgsize-49446.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Fcold-blooded-murder-priyanka-gandhi-slams-israel-says-genocide-of-palestinian-people-shows-humanity-means-nothing-to-them%2Farticleshow%2F119212573.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Congress%20MP%20Priyanka%20Gandhi%20Vadra%20criticised%20the%20Israeli%20government%20for%20the%20%26quot%3Bcold-blooded%20murder%26quot%3B%20of%20over%20400%20Palestinian%20civilians%2C%20including%20children%2C%20emphasizing%20that%20such%20acts%20re