ashi%20Tharoor%20instead%20of%20Speaking%20against%20PM%20Modi%20and%20the%20nation%20every%20time...%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%20and%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20should%20come%20forward%20and%20appreciate%20Shashi%20Tharoor's%20stand%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Patra%20told%20reporters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20post%20on%20X%2C%20formerly%20Twitter%2C%20Kerala%20BJP%20chief%20K%20Surendran%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BDear%20Shashi%20Tharoor%20ji%2C%20I've%20always%20admired%20your%20candour.%20Your%20honesty%20in%20saying%2C%20'I%20opposed%20it%20initially'%20and%20now%20praising%20Modiplomacy's%20success%20in%20Russia-Ukraine%20is%20commendable.%20Unlike%20your%20INC%20peers%2C%20you%20see%20India's%20global%20rise%20under%20PM%20Narendra%20Modi%20is%20truly%20a%20refreshing%20take%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20--%20which%20warned%20against%20out-of-turn%20comments%20last%20month%20after%20Mr%20Tharoor's%20praise%20of%20certain%20policies%20of%20the%20CPM%20in%20Kerala%20--%20has%20maintained%20silence.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20a%20meeting%20last%20month%2C%20the%20upset%20party%20took%20a%20conscious%20decision%20not%20to%20react%20the%20Thiruvananthapuram%20MP's%20comments%20and%20maintain%20its%20focus%20on%20Kerala's%20ruling%20LDF%20government%20in%20view%20of%20the%20coming%20state%20elections.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Tharoor%20-%20a%20former%20Union%20minister%20and%20a%20four-time%20MP%20from%20Thiruvananthapuram%20--%20had%20clarified%20that%20he%20was%20highlighting%20Kerala's%20progress%20in%20the%20start-up%20sector.%20He%20also%20made%20it%20clear%20that%20he%20would%20pursue%20his%20own%20interests%20in%20terms%20of%20his%20writing%20and%20lectures%20if%20the%20party%20did%20not%20want%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20at%20the%20Raisina%20Dialogue%20yesterday%2C%20Mr%20Tharoor%20had%20admitted%20that%20he%20had%20misjudged%20India's%20position%20on%20the%20Russia-Ukraine%20conflict.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20am%20still%20wiping%20the%20egg%20off%20my%20face%20because%20I%20was%20one%20of%20those%20who%20criticised%20India's%20position%20back%20in%20February%202022.%20Three%20years%20later%2C%20it%20turns%20out%20I%20was%20wrong.%20India%20now%20has%20a%20Prime%20Minister%20who%20can%20hug%20both%20the%20President%20of%20Ukraine%20and%20the%20President%20of%20Russia%20within%20two%20weeks%20and%20still%20be%20accepted%20in%20both%20places.%20That%20means%20India%20is%20in%20a%20position%20to%20make%20a%20difference%20to%20lasting%20peace%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EQuestioned%20about%20his%20comments%20earlier%20today%2C%20Mr%20Tharoor%20reaffirmed%20his%20stand%20and%20said%20there%20was%20nothing%20to%20add.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERussia%20invaded%20Ukraine%20on%20February%2024%2C%202022%20and%20despite%20the%20pressure%20to%20condemn%20Russian%20President%20Vladimir%20Putin's%20move%2C%20India%20had%20taken%20a%20nuanced%20stand.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1742385480000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-08%2F2ph2j96g_shashi-tharoor_625x300_30_August_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbjp-jubilant-congress-silent-over-shashi-tharoors-egg-on-face-comment-7960326%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Senior%20Congress%20leader%20and%20former%20diplomat%20Shashi%20Tharoor's%20%26quot%3Begg%20on%20my%20face%26quot%3B%20comment%20acknowledging%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi's%20diplomatic%20stance%20on%20the%20Russia-Ukraine%20hostilities%2C%20has%20brought%20much%20delight%20to%20the%20BJP%20camp.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbjp-jubilant-congress-silent-over-shashi-tharoors-egg-on-face-comment-7960326%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Naseer%20Soomro%2C%20Pakistan's%20Tallest%20Man%2C%20Dies%20At%2055%20After%20Prolonged%20Illness%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EPakistan's%20tallest%20man%2