n%20cement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-03%2Fhscmpeq8_meerut-cement-murder_625x300_19_March_25.jpg%3Fim%3DFitAndFill%2Calgorithm%3Ddnn%2Cwidth%3D1200%2Cheight%3D738%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMessages%20From%20The%20Dead%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENDTV%20has%20accessed%20the%20WhatsApp%20messages%20Chinki%20received%20from%20Saurabh's%20number.%20On%20March%206%2C%20a%20message%20asked%20if%20Chinki%20would%20be%20in%20Meerut%20for%20Holi.%20When%20she%20said%20yes%2C%20the%20reply%20was%20that%20he%20was%20out%20and%20would%20only%20return%20after%20the%20festival.%20Two%20days%20later%2C%20on%20March%208%2C%20she%20asked%20if%20he%20did%20not%20take%20his%20daughter%20with%20him.%20The%20reply%20was%20that%20the%20temperature%20where%20he%20had%20gone%20was%20-10%20degrees%20Celsius%20and%20she%20would%20have%20been%20ill.%20Holi%20wishes%20were%20also%20exchanged.%20The%20day%20after%20Holi%2C%20March%2015%2C%20Chinki%20asked%20when%20Saurabh%20would%20return%20as%20she%20was%20about%20to%20leave.%20The%20reply%20was%20he%20had%20a%20party%20planned%20and%20was%20not%20sure%20when%20he%20would%20be%20back%20in%20Meerut.%20Chinki%20asked%20her%20brother%20to%20enjoy%20himself.%20In%20turn%2C%20she%20was%20asked%20how%20the%20Holi%20at%20home%20was.%20On%20March%2016%2C%20Chinki%20called%20over%20WhatsApp%2C%20hoping%20to%20speak%20to%20Saurabh.%20The%20call%20went%20unanswered.%20The%20next%20day%2C%20four%20calls%20went%20unanswered.%20The%20family%20grew%20suspicious%20and%20approached%20the%20police.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20questioning%2C%20it%20was%20revealed%20that%20Muskaan%20and%20Sahil%20travelled%20to%20Himachal%20shortly%20after%20Saurabh's%20murder.%20They%20took%20his%20phone%20along%20and%20posted%20photos%20and%20video