0wanted%20to%20stay%2C%20so%20we%20agreed%20that%20I%20would%20move%20to%20live%20with%20her%20after%20I%20graduated.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'd%20lived%20in%20Armenia%20for%20a%20couple%20of%20months%20in%202023%20as%20part%20of%20a%20Russian%20language%20immersion%20program%2C%20and%20couldn't%20have%20been%20more%20excited%20to%20live%20there%20again.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%228d0dd6fb-7d5b-411f-8f0a-ddc870fc62d5%5C%22%3EI%20had%20no%20paying%20job%20lined%20up%20when%20I%20landed%20in%20Armenia%2C%20and%20neither%20did%20my%20partner%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20plan%20was%20that%20she%20was%20going%20to%20volunteer%20with%20Birthright%20Armenia%2C%20and%20I%20would%20volunteer%20with%20the%20Armenian%20Volunteer%20Corps.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20were%20only%20paying%20%24275%20(before%20utilities)%20for%20a%20one-bedroom%20in%20Vanadzor%2C%20the%20third-largest%20city%20in%20Armenia.%20However%2C%20since%20we%20were%20both%20volunteering%2C%20we%20were%20not%20making%20money%20and%2C%20after%20a%20few%20months%2C%20were%20running%20low%20on%20funds%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fbanking%2Fhow-to-save-money%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efrom%20our%20savings%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20top%20of%20that%2C%20there%20were%20the%20challenges%20of%20living%20with%20a%20partner%20for%20the%20first%20time.%20While%20growing%20pains%20are%20normal%2C%20moving%20in%20together%20in%20a%20country%20where%20you%20are%20still%20learning%20the%20customs%20and%20unfamiliar%20with%20the%20language%20adds%20an%20entirely%20new%20dimension%20of%20stress.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20often%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsolo-travel-woman-scared-emigrated-alone-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efelt%20isolated%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20led%20to%20multiple%20disagreements%20over%20how%20to%20address%20the%20situation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2263ec8a66-5714-457d-941e-ed63fdd11959%5C%22%3EDespite%20these%20challenges%2C%20we%20overcame%20them%20by%20being%20proactive%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20start%20of%202025%2C%20we%20moved%20to%20Yerevan%2C%20the%20capital%2C%20and%20landed%20full-time%20jobs%20in%20our%20respective%20fields.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20are%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmove-uk-to-us-american-work-culture-never-adjust-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Enot%20making%20as%20much%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20we%20would%20back%20in%20the%20US%2C%20but%20we%20are%20spending%20far%20less.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlthough%20the%20cost%20of%20living%20in%20Yerevan%20has%20risen%20over%20the%20years%2C%20it%20is%20still%20substantially%20low%20compared%20to%20Boston%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-expensive-is-new-york-city-mind-blowing-facts-2019-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENew%20York%20City%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAn%20average%20night%20out%20to%20dinner%20and%20multiple%20drinks%20costs%20%2430%20to%20%2450.%20However%2C%20I%20can%20also%20get%20shawarma%20the%20size%20of%20my%20head%20for%20under%20%243.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20we%20spend%20our%20weekends%20exploring%20the%20country%20we%20have%20loved%20for%20so%20long.%20We've%20explored%20the%20%26quot%3Bfairy%20tale%20province%26quot%3B%20of%20Lori%20and%20skied%20in%20Tsaghkadzor.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20also%20started%20taking%20private%20Russian%20lessons%20online%20(most%20Armenians%20speak%20Russian)%2C%20and%20my%20Armenian%20has%20improved.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22fde3dd65-e92d-4d08-8767-624d92cc1761%5C%22%3EThe%20kindness%20I%20have%20experienced%20from%20strangers%20in%20Armenia%20is%20simply%20unmatched%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20have%20traveled%20extensively%2C%20and%20most%20of%20the%20locals%20are%20friendly%20in%20countries%20I%20have%20been%20to%2C%20but%20if%20I%20were%20to%20rank%20them%20by%20friendliness%2C%20then%20Armenia%20would%20be%20No.%201.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELast%20month%2C%20I%20accidentally%20took%20the%20wrong%20bus%20to%20work%20and%20got%20stranded.%20Conveniently%2C%20my%20phone%20stopped%20working%2C%20and%20I%20was%20visibly%20upset.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20group%20of%20women%20standing%20nearby%20asked%20me%20what%20was%20wrong.%20I%20told%20them%20(in%20broken%20Russian%2C%20no%20less)%20of%20my%20predicament.%20One%20of%20the%20women%20called%20her%20daughter%2C%20who%20spoke%20English.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20told%20the%20daughter%20where%20I%20worked%2C%20it%20just%20so%20happened%20that%20her%20mother%20worked%20close%20by.%20They%20insisted%20on%20ordering%20me%20a%20taxi%2C%20refusing%20any%20cash%20offer%20I%20made%20as%20a%20token%20of%20thanks%2C%20and%20giving%20me%20chocolate%20as%20a%20parting%20gift.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESuch%20acts%20of%20kindness%20are%20a%20common%20experience%20in%20Armenia.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%220c653229-c16f-481c-b1cc-fb9f51b772ec%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EWe%20dated%20long-distance%20for%203%20years%2C%20and%20we%20could%20not%20wait%20for%20the%20day%20to%20be%20together%20in%20the%20same%20place%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ESeeing%20Mount%20Ararat%20every%20morning%20never%20gets%20old%2C%20but%20I%20have%20longed%20to%20fall%20asleep%20and%20wake%20up%20next%20to%20my%20partner%20%E2%80%94%20nothing%20compares%20to%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThroughout%20everything%2C%20she%20has%20made%20me%20stronger.%20I%20only%20hope%20she%20feels%20the%20same.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20don't%20know%20what%20the%20future%20holds%20for%20the%20two%20of%20us%2C%20but%20I%20know%20we%20are%20both%20happy%20we%20decided%20to%20start%20a%20new%20chapter%20of%20our%20lives%20here.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20moved%20to%20Armenia%20to%20live%20with%20my%20partner%2C%20but%20now%20that%20we%20have%20stable%20jobs%20in%20a%20city%20with%20a%20low%20cost%20of%20living%20and%20get%20the%20chance%20to%20see%20the%20country's%20breathtaking%20beauty%20almost%20every%20weekend%2C%20we%20don't%20have%20a%20plan%20to%20leave%20anytime