nceive%2C%20Kidnaps%20Child%20From%20Jaipur%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20Rajasthan%20couple%20who%20were%20struggling%20to%20conceive%20allegedly%20kidnapped%20a%20four-year-old%20boy%20from%20Jaipur%20railway%20station%20last%20week.%20The%20couple%20carried%20the%20boy%20away%20to%20raise%20him%20as%20their%20own%2C%20police%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESundar%20Kashyap%20and%20Jeevika%2C%20both%2028%20years%20old%2C%20kidnapped%20the%20toddler%2C%20Shivam%2C%20when%20he%20and%20his%20mother%2C%20Priyanka%2C%20were%20waiting%20for%20a%20train.%20The%20kidnapping%20was%20caught%20on%20CCTV%20cameras%20installed%20at%20the%20station.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20evening%20of%20March%2014%2C%20Priyanka%20and%20her%20three%20children%20were%20on%20their%20way%20to%20her%20parent's%20house%20in%20Siwan%2C%20Bihar%2C%20when%20Jeevika%20lured%20Shivam.%20The%20accused%20pair%20then%20got%20on%20a%20bus%20at%20Narayan%20Singh%20Circle%20heading%20for%20Uttar%20Pradesh.%20Following%20a%20nightlong%20search%20for%20Shivam%2C%20his%20parents-%20both%20daily-wage%20workers-%20filed%20a%20complaint%20with%20GRP%20on%20March%2015.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEverything%20was%20caught%20on%20CCTV%2C%20which%20helped%20us%20track%20the%20accused%2C%26quot%3B%20SHO%20Arun%20Chaudhary%20of%20the%20GRP%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Police%20detained%20the%20young%20couple%20from%20Mahuwa%20in%20the%20Dausa%20district%20of%20Rajasthan%20two%20days%20later.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20GRP%20eventually%20located%20the%20couple%20and%20returned%20the%20child%20to%20his%20parents%20within%2048%20hours.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20child%20was%20found%20safe%20and%20the%20accused%20were%20taken%20into%20custody%20when%20police%20arrived%20at%20their%20address%20on%20Sunday%20and%20searched%20the%20house.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAjmer%20GRP%20DSP%20Narender%20Singh%20noted%20that%20Jeevika%2C%20a%20mother%20of%20two%2C%20had%20been%20living%20with%20Kashyap%2C%20a%20worker%20who%20earned%20a%20daily%20wage%2C%20since%20leaving%20her%20husband.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20was%20unable%20to%20conceive%20due%20to%20a%20%26quot%3Bsterilisation%20procedure.%26quot%3B%20Singh%20added%20that%20the%20couple%20%26quot%3Btried%20medical%20options%20to%20have%20a%20child%20but%20failed%2C%20and%20they%20plotted%20to%20kidnap%20a%20child%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Times%20of%20India%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20couple%20had%20been%20preparing%20to%20kidnap%20a%20child%20for%20almost%20eight%20months%20and%20had%20spent%20hours%20conducting%20research%20at%20the%20train%20station%20before%20carrying%20out%20their%20plot%2C%20the%20investigation%20revealed.%20The%20couple%20reportedly%20packed%20clothes%2C%20snacks%2C%20and%20milk%20in%20a%20bag%20when%20they%20travelled%20to%20the%20train%20station%20to%20carry%20out%20the%20kidnapping.%20They%20took%20a%20bus%20to%20Mahuwa%20after%20kidnapping%20the%20youngster.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKashyap%20and%20Jeevika%20intended%20to%20name%20the%20boy%20and%20even%20considered%20calling%20him%20Ashish%2C%20police%20said.%20%26quot%3BJeevika%20insisted%20the%20boy%20call%20her%20'mummy'.%20The%20accused%20couple%20was%20arrested%20under%20BNS%20Section%20137(2)%20for%20kidnapping%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20DSP%20Singh.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1742377620000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-03%2Frdgie00g_rajasthan_625x300_19_March_25.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Funable-to-conceive-rajasthan-couple-kidnaps-child-from-jaipur-railway-station-7957829%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20couple%20reportedly%20packed%20clothes%2C%20snacks%2C%20and%20milk%20in%20a%20bag%20when%20they%20travelled%20to%20the%20train%20station%20to%20carry%20out%20the%20kidnapping.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Funable-to-conceive-rajasthan-couple-kidnaps-child-from-jaipur-railway-station-7957829%22%2C