20released%2C%20the%20authorities%20still%20have%20his%20passport%2C%20which%20they%20confiscated%20last%20week.%20Mr%20Riibe's%20attorney%2C%20Beatriz%20Santana%2C%20said%20they%20were%20requesting%20a%20new%20passport%20with%20the%20US%20Embassy.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Konanki%20was%20last%20seen%20at%20the%20Riu%20Republic%20Resort%20in%20Punta%20Cana%20town%20on%20March%206.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2020-year-old%2C%20accompanied%20by%20five%20friends%2C%20went%20out%20to%20party%20at%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fnew-video-shows-indian-american-student-sudiksha-konanki-at-bar-with-joshua-riibe-before-going-missing-7943407%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPunta%20Cana%20resort%20nightclub%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20the%20evening%20of%20March%205.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Konanki%20and%20Mr%20Riibe%20were%20seen%20together%20at%20an%20outdoor%20bar%20before%20she%20vanished%20from%20a%20beach%20on%20March%206.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESurveillance%20footage%20captured%20them%20at%20the%20club%20before%20heading%20to%20the%20beach%20at%20around%204%3A15%20am.%20Most%20of%20Ms%20Konanki's%20friends%20left%20by%205%3A50%20am%2C%20leaving%20her%20alone%20with%20Mr%20Riibe.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20clip%20from%20the%20Riu%20Republica%20Resort%20showed%20the%20woman%20walking%20arm-in-arm%20with%20the%20man%2C%20along%20a%20resort%20pathway.%20They%20were%20accompanied%20by%20her%20friends%20in%20the%20video.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Riibe%2C%20who%20was%20in%20custody%20since%20Ms%20Konanki's%20disappearance%2C%20told%20investigators%20he%20was%20with%20her%20in%20waist-deep%20water%2C%20when%20a%20strong%20wave%20pulled%20them%20out%20to%20sea.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20he%20tried%20to%20hold%20Ms%20Konanki%20under%20his%20arm%20while%20swimming%20back%20to%20shore.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Riibe%20last%20asked%20if%20she%20was%20okay%20but%20didn't%20hear%20her%20response.%20He%20began%20vomiting%20seawater%20and%20black