%20Rs%203%2C400%20crore%2C%20according%20to%20a%20report%20released%20by%20the%20Association%20for%20Democratic%20Reforms%20(ADR).%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Findias-richest-mla-has-rs-3-400-crore-in-assets-poorest-just-rs-1-700-7958583%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Rohit%20Snubbed%20As%20Hardik%20Names%20His%20Captaincy%20Replacement%20For%20CSK%20Clash%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ESuryakumar%20Yadav%20will%20captain%20Mumbai%20Indians%20in%20their%20opening%20IPL%20match%20against%20Chennai%20Super%20Kings%20on%20Sunday%20as%20regular%20skipper%20Hardik%20Pandya%20will%20be%20forced%20to%20sit%20out%20due%20to%20a%20one-match%20suspension%20for%20over-rate%20offences%20committed%20by%20the%20team%20last%20season.%20Suryakumar%20is%20the%20national%20T20%20captain%20and%20recently%20led%20the%20side%20to%20a%204-1%20triumph%20over%20England%20at%20home.%20However%2C%20his%20batting%20form%20wasn't%20particularly%20impressive%20and%20he%20managed%20just%2038%20runs%20in%20the%20five%20outings%20during%20the%20series.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSurya%20leads%20India%20as%20well.%20When%20I%20am%20not%20there%20he%20is%20the%20ideal%20choice%2C%26quot%3B%20Pandya%20said%20during%20MI's%20pre-season%20press%20conference%20here.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMI%20head%20coach%20Mahela%20Jayawardene%20said%20the%20BCCI%20has%20communicated%20the%20one-match%20ban%20on%20Pandya%20to%20the%20team%20owing%20to%20three%20slow%20over-rate%20violations%20by%20his%20team%20last%20season.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMI%20had%20finished%20at%20the%20bottom%20of%20the%20heap%2C%20managing%20just%20four%20wins%20against%2010%20losses%20in%202024%2C%20which%20was%20Pandya's%20debut%20year%20as%20captain.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20took%20over%20from%20Rohit%20Sharma%2C%20who%20led%20the%20side%20to%20five%20trophies%20but%20was%20struggling%20at%20that%20stage.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJayawardene%20did%20not%20give%20a%20time%20frame%20for%20Jasprit%20Bumrah's%20return%20to%20competitive%20cricket%2C%20and%20said%20the%20pace%20spearhead's%20absence%20will%20be%20a%20massive%20%26quot%3Bchallenge%26quot%3B%20for%20his%20side%20in%20the%20IPL%202025.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBumrah%20will%20miss%20a%20few%20initial%20games%20of%20the%20tournament%20as%20he%20is%20currently%20recuperating%20from%20a%20back%20injury%20at%20the%20BCCI%20Centre%20of%20Excellence%20at%20Bengaluru.%20%26quot%3BJasprit%20Bumrah%20is%20at%20the%20NCA.%20We%20have%20to%20wait%20and%20see%20their%20feedback%20on%20him.%20At%20the%20moment%20it%20is%20going%20well%2C%20the%20progress%20is%20on%20a%20day%20to%20day%20basis%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Jayawardene%20during%20MI's%20pre-season%20press%20meet%20here%20on%20Wednesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20is%20in%20good%20spirits%2C%20and%20not%20having%20him%20is%20a%20challenge.%20He%20is%20the%20best%20bowler%20in%20the%20world%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added..%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBumrah%20has%20been%20sidelined%20since%20the%20final%20Test%20against%20Australia%20at%20Sydney%20in%20early%20January%2C%20when%20he%20could%20not%20bowl%20in%20the%20second%20innings%20as%20the%20hosts%20chased%20down%20162%20to%20seal%20a%203-1%20series%20victory.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBumrah's%20return%20is%20shrouded%20in%20uncertainty%20but%20MI%20skipper%20Hardik%20Pandya%20said%20having%20an%20experienced%20campaigner%20like%20the%2030-year-old%20in%20the%20dressing%20room%20will%20help%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBumrah%20is%20expected%20to%20link%20with%20Mumbai%20colleagues%20in%20the%20first%20week%20of%20April%20and%20could%20continue%20his%20rehabilitation%20with%20the%20team.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20am%20lucky%20that%20I%20have%20three%20captains%20playing%20with%20me%20-%20Rohit%2C%20Surya%20and%20Bumrah.%20They%20always%20place%20an%20arm%20around%20my%20shoulder%20and%20are%20there%20when%20I%20need%20any%20