school%20dropouts%20is%20widespread.%20According%20to%20official%20data%20from%20the%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20government%2C%20the%20tribal%20community%20and%20other%20marginalised%20communities%20have%20the%20highest%20school%20dropout%20rate%20at%20the%20secondary%20level%2C%20with%2014.17%25.%20This%20includes%2019.05%25%20among%20girls%20and%2010.55%25%20among%20boys.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%227521127830%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfshana%20Gul%2C%20a%20teacher%20in%20Uri%2C%20North%20Kashmir%2C%20has%20witnessed%20this%20harsh%20reality%20firsthand.%20%E2%80%9CNo%20one%20wants%20to%20drop%20out%20of%20school%2C%20but%20financial%20hardships%20force%20many%20to%20do%20so%2C%20especially%20girls.%20It%20is%20heartbreaking%20to%20see%20bright%20students%20leave%20their%20education%20midway%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%20%E2%80%9CAs%20a%20teacher%2C%20nothing%20hurts%20you%20more%20than%20seeing%20one%20of%20your%20bright%20students%20drop%20out%20midway.%20Some%20of%20my%20best%20students%20from%20three%20years%20ago%20are%20now%20at%20home%2C%20unable%20to%20continue%20their%20studies.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20the%20challenges%2C%20Malik%20remains%20determined.%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20your%20intentions%20are%20clear%2C%20there%20will%20be%20support%20for%20you%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%20His%20initiative%20runs%20entirely%20on%20crowdfunding%2C%20with%20people%20contributing%20small%20amounts%20%E2%80%94%20Rs%20100%2C%20Rs%20200%2C%20or%20Rs%20500%20per%20month.%20%E2%80%9CNow%20people%20have%20trust%20in%20me%2C%20and%20these%20small%20contributions%2C%20though%20minimal%20for%20them%2C%20help%20us%20enrol%20students%20and%20fulfil%20their%20dreams.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThere%E2%80%99s%20no%20support%20for%20us%20from%20the